main event: Several civilians reported seeing a luminous object described as a red sphere with four jet engines in the sky over Safi, Morocco, on February 8, 1966.
interesting points: The object was moving at a very low altitude and very high speed,The object lit up the entire district as it passed overhead,Multiple trustworthy witnesses confirmed the sighting,The meteorology station in Safi corroborated the presence of the object,The object appeared to have the shape of a sphere with four wings.
sighted object: luminous sphere with four jet engines
witness description: civilians in front of a restaurant at the angle of Portugal and Quassel Road
